This is a Lorem Ipsum Generator Tool. If there are any glaring issues I missed, or features to add - etc, please do not hesitate to submit a pull request. Thanks!


Created By: Joseph Kesselring | twitter @jkesselring

Purpose: To aid in providing Lorem Ipsum filler text programatically. 

Thanks to: http://www.lipsum.com/ for their awesome web based lorem ipsum generation service. 

Use: see index.php for a sample page.

Essentially: Require generator.php, feed it a format(html, blank or text for text) and a length. Length is number of 'paragraphs' you wish to pull into the page. 

Planned: 
